---
title: "About"
description: "Learn about the ISC2 Tampa Bay Chapter, our mission, and our leadership team."
layout: base.njk
---

  <!-- Page Header -->
  <div class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>About</h1>
      <p class="page-header-subtitle">Who we are, what we do, and who runs the thing.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- About the Chapter -->
  <section class="split-section">
    <div class="container split-grid">
      <div class="split-text">
        <span class="section-label">About Our Chapter</span>
        <h2>About the ISC2 Tampa Bay Chapter</h2>
        <p>We're a local chapter of ISC2 for security professionals in the Tampa Bay area. We meet quarterly, share what we know, and help each other out. You don't need an ISC2 certification to join. If you work in security or want to, you're welcome.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="split-media">
        <img src="/images/meeting2.jpeg" alt="ISC2 Tampa Bay chapter meeting" style="border-radius:var(--radius-lg);box-shadow:var(--shadow-md);">
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About ISC2 -->
  <section class="content-section" style="background: var(--light-gray);">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-label">About ISC2</span>
      <h2>About ISC2</h2>
      <p>ISC2 is the international nonprofit behind certifications like CISSP and SSCP. They have over 140,000 certified members worldwide.</p>
      <p>ISC2's certifications are among the first information technology credentials to meet the stringent requirements of ANSI/ISO/IEC Standard 17024, a global benchmark for assessing and certifying personnel. ISC2 also offers a variety of education programs and services based on its CBK&reg;, a compendium of information security topics. Education offerings consist of classroom and online review seminars, self assessment tools, and textbooks. More information is available at <a href="https://www.isc2.org/aboutus">www.isc2.org/aboutus</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Leadership Team -->
  <section class="content-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <span class="section-label">Our Team</span>
        <h2>Our Leadership Team</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="leadership-grid">
        {%- for person in leadership %}
        <div class="leader animate-on-scroll">
          <a href="{{ person.linkedin }}">
            <img src="{{ person.image }}" alt="{{ person.name }}">
            <h3>{{ person.name }}</h3>
            <p class="title">{{ person.title if person.title else "&nbsp;" | safe }}</p>
          </a>
        </div>
        {%- endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
